main event: Observers at Kirtland AFB witnessed a star-like object traveling toward the SSE for 3-4 minutes.
interesting points: The object appeared to gain altitude as it moved,Initially moving slowly, it then picked up speed,The object veered to the left and right before returning to its original position,Investigators concluded it was the Echo II satellite,The sighting occurred on July 12, 1966 around 0432.
